    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9SF6KY1EAQ17VRHQQAWX\">Added</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>​<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-37608\">LCD-37608</a> - Download Scaling Reports:</strong> Added a button on the Scale page to download scaling reports, allowing users to quickly access historic scaling data.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9NRE5H6PTZ9Y99PF8QQH\">Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul class=\"ak-ul\">\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-37609\">LCD-37609</a> - Metrics for Redeployed Services:</strong> Fixed an issue where CPU and memory metrics from previously deployed Search and Liferay services weren't available after redeploying the services.</li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-38293\">LCD-38293</a> - Fixed Sidebar Tab Issue:</strong> Fixed an issue where the Settings tab was no longer selected after navigating to other tabs within the Settings page.</li>\n</ul>"
      },
